block content
  // Google Map
  #map.map
  // -/map
  // End Google Map
  // === Content Part ===
  .container.content
    .row.margin-bottom-30
      .col-md-9.mb-margin-bottom-30
        .headline
          h2 Contact Form
        p
          | At vero eos et accusamus et iusto odio dignissimos ducimus qui blanditiis praesentium voluptatum deleniti atque corrupti quos dolores et quas feugiat. Et harum quidem rerum facilis est et expedita distinctio lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit landitiis.
        br
        form#sky-form3.sky-form.contact-style(action='assets/php/sky-forms-pro/demo-contacts-process.php', method='post')
          fieldset.no-padding
            label
              | Name
              span.color-red *
            .row.sky-space-20
              .col-md-7.col-md-offset-0
                div
                  input#name.form-control(type='text', name='name')
            label
              | Email
              span.color-red *
            .row.sky-space-20
              .col-md-7.col-md-offset-0
                div
                  input#email.form-control(type='text', name='email')
            label
              | Message
              span.color-red *
            .row.sky-space-20
              .col-md-11.col-md-offset-0
                div
                  textarea#message.form-control(rows='8', name='message')
            p
              button.btn-u(type='submit') Send Message
          .message
            i.rounded-x.fa.fa-check
            p Your message was successfully sent!
      // /col-md-9
      .col-md-3
        // Contacts
        .headline
          h2 Contacts
        ul.list-unstyled.who.margin-bottom-30
          li
            a(href='#')
              i.fa.fa-home
              | 5B Streat, City 50987 New Town US
          li
            a(href='#')
              i.fa.fa-envelope
              | info@example.com
          li
            a(href='#')
              i.fa.fa-phone
              | 1(222) 5x86 x97x
          li
            a(href='#')
              i.fa.fa-globe
              | http://www.example.com
        // Business Hours
        .headline
          h2 Business Hours
        ul.list-unstyled.margin-bottom-30
          li
            strong Monday-Friday:
            |  10am to 8pm
          li
            strong Saturday:
            |  11am to 3pm
          li
            strong Sunday:
            |  Closed
        // Why we are?
        .headline
          h2 Why we are?
        p
          | At vero eos et accusamus et iusto odio dignissimos ducimus qui blanditiis praesentium voluptatum.
        ul.list-unstyled
          li
            i.fa.fa-check.color-green
            |  Odio dignissimos ducimus
          li
            i.fa.fa-check.color-green
            |  Blanditiis praesentium volup
          li
            i.fa.fa-check.color-green
            |  Eos et accusamus
      // /col-md-3
    // /row
  // /container
  // === End Content Part ===
